name: 5 mazes: Master levels
description:
The current program version is 5 mazes: Master levels  v1.0 with the latest changes dated 2023-03-07.

Controls

Start the game: Enter

Movement: arrows or WASD

Interact/confirm dialog: Alt, Z or J

Game

Get through five consecutive mazes, larger and more difficult than in the previous games.

Credits

Game idea and GB Studio magic: godai.

Mazes generated with maze generating algorithm by Keesie Meijer.

Music tracks by AJ Booker.

This is a sequel to 5 more mazes and 5 more mazes.
